description:
You are the naughty cat.

Get ready to cause chaos in Cat From Hell, where you take control of a naughty cat determined to drive Granny crazy! Whether it's eating the fish from the aquarium, breaking flower pots, or throwing random items across the room, Cat From Hell lets you do it all.

Scratch carpets, couches, and any furniture in sight as you explore different rooms filled with destructible objects. With every mess you make, Granny’s patience runs thinner—how far can you push her in Cat From Hell?

Features:
★ Interactive environments full of destructible items;
★ Hilarious reactions from Granny as you wreak havoc;
★ Endless opportunities for mischievous behavior;
★ Simple, fun, and addictive gameplay.

Play Cat From Hell now and start your journey as the ultimate troublemaking cat!
